content.detailedDescription:
I was walking through my apt towards the windows. as i looked out the window i noticed a bright object in the eastern sky. i said to my wife: 'what is that?!" it looked at first like a meteor burning up upon entering the atmosphere, i know this as i have seen that before, and i thought wow the looks really close and got worried because it looked really close. it looked like it was on fire. by now my wife was there with me and she was in total disbelief, and kept asking what is that?. but then as we watched, i was expecting it to pass over us and continue towards the city, nyc, which is just west of my bldg across the east river, it made a 9o degree left turn, and continued on a steady path. no longer a meteor!? this made get my phone and start recording this. so i open the window to get a clearer view, and started recording. i recorded about 30 seconds, until the object went through some clouds and disappeared. 

we live in the flight path for landing airplanes at laguardia airport. planes fly through all the time. from south to north. this object crossed this path from east to west and then turned from west to south east.

this was the day after the snow storm, there was also a near full moon.
content.summary: Was looking out 5th floor east facing window, saw an object with looked like it was on fire, as i watched it it changed direction, was pulsating, round, not a comet.

content.detailedDescription:
just throwing this out there, at approx 6:09pm eastern time january 23rd 2016 my wife and i were driving home from niles michigan to dowagiac michigan. i noticed that as the full moon inched above the treeline, the moon appeared very large. i made comment about wanting a telescope to view it. minutes later i saw a black line crossing the face of the moon. the line covered approx 5% of the visable moon, refrencing the moon to a clock, the line began at 10 o'clock and move toward the 4 o'clock position. the "front" of the line was rounded. i pointed it to my wife. she stated that from the angle and its position it was not a powerline. we watched as we drove, the line completly crossed the moon's face and seconds afterward the "tail" appeared moving from 10 o'clock to the 4 o'clock position. the line remained straight the entire time and moved in uniform speed.


as the tail moved away from the moon's face it dissapeared. my wife and i began rationalizing what we just saw trying to explain it away, but could not. a few minutes later, the line reappeared at the 1 o'clock position. the size had not changed and the angle it traveled across the moon face was the same. this time it decended from 1 o'clock to its original position between 10 and 4. it only covered the right half of the moon during this transit. when it reached its original position between 10 and 4, it exited via the 4 o'clock position.


once we lost sight of the silhouette second time it never returned.
content.summary: Object appeared as a silhouette in front of the moon

content.detailedDescription: About 4 years ago myself and my work colleague were traveling on counrty roads through lincolnshire in the uk. we were heading straight into a big thunder storm with a lot of lightening happening infront of us as we drove into the storm area. i was the passenger in the car and so i took my phone out of my pocket and tried to catch a flash of lighting as my colleague drove into the storm. i took 3 photo's but i was very  disapointed because i did not catch one flash of lightening. it was many months latter when i looked again at the 3 photo,s on my phone before deleting them, thats when i noticed a stange shape / anomaly in one of the photo,s. i have to say at the time of taking the photo's nothing could been seen in the sky apart from the intence lightening straight ahead. i saved these 3 photo,s to my pc and thats were they have stayed ever since. i was unsure what do with this photo ???? once i let it go on line its just out there, thats why i am writing to you now. your site and your seem's to credit the people who see and film these strange anomalys. this not a fake photo, i am not smart enough on a pc to even try anything like that.As you can see there is nothing on the other 2 photo's taken at the same time, its strange ? i did send this picture to a well know youtube site some months ago at their request but i never heard anything back from them, i hope you might be able to use this picture or maybe identify what it could be in the photo.

content.detailedDescription:
I am a photographer and went out to take some night shots of a windmill in a small village outside my home town.
i had my camera on a tripod taking photos of the windmill and stars in the night sky, it was a clear night very cold out, i was taking various exposures of the windmill to try and get one showing the stars but without showing star trials, when all of a sudden a large triangle ufo flew over slightly to my left, it was dark and very low, but no noise at all, it had little lights in each corner red/orange colour, my first thoughts was a military aircraft, but it definitely was not a stealth aircraft as this was a proper triangle shape i would say equal lengths on each side, it flew with point first manner, as thinking it may have been military i headed to the nearest air force base in coningsby lincolnshire, but when i got there the base was quiet, nothing going off and no sign of the ufo, after speaking with friends i have come to believe this not to be any military aircraft know to anyone, this is either technology we do not know of, or some form of alien craft.
i myself am not convinced of alien visits, but do not rule anything out, therefore i am thinking it is military technology that is being withheld, whether this technology is alien or not i can't agree or disagree.
due to my camera being on a tripod and the fact that photographing a moving object at night only gets you mostly a blurred image unless flash light is used to light it up, so unfortunately didn't capture any images.
content.summary: Silent triangle ufo flew over with small lights in corners

content.detailedDescription:
I was walking my dog near my home as i always do at the same time every evening.
the area is a park in front of my house. 
it was snowing with no wind and it was a full moon so it was quite bright with the reflection 
of moonlight off the snow.
snow was falling straight down to the ground. i was on why way back to my home when i heard a roaring sound coming from my left side(north side) i looked but could see nothing.
i heard it go over my head but could still see nothing until it passed to my right side. at that moment i saw a translucent boomerang shape with about a three meter wing span flying directly south towards a large fir tree. it was about two meters above my head and i only noticed it because of the trail of snow going over the objects sharp angled wings. i am certain the object was invisible apart from this.
i was in a state of shock. i took the dog home and went back because i was sure it must have hit the fir tree. but could find nothing. 
i told my wife and a few friends about it but most mostly laughed at so i haven't really spoken to anybody about it since for fear of being ridiculed.
it's been a few years since the sighting and i can't remember the exact year and month.
content.summary: Invisible ufo observed due to snow fall passing over it.

well we where coming upon to a stop sign where we cross to get on the same side as the store.We noticed the street light. the light of the pole was not where it was suppose to be. it was bouncing and swaying on the outside. kinda like those paddles with the ball attached. we didn't cross we just started at it for a bit. i turned to my daughter and said you see that. she said yes and we started crossing the road. as we did the light stopped moving and went into the pole where the light was suppose to be. we looked at each other like how did it do that. we walked under it looking up at it and it had a cover. 
we became very puzzled and worried because we were the only ones out at that moment. we just wanted to get to the store. i first thought of was tinkerbell. i'm so puzzled on what we saw. i need some sort of explanation or insight of what happen. i tried google search, youtube,ect to see if anyone else ever had a sighting like this before. i can't find anything similar to what we seen. what was flying around this street light?

content.detailedDescription:
I had just pulled into my apartment complex at approximately 12am. i noticed from my drivers side something shadowy move to the north over the apartments. i parked my car, got out and looked towards the orion belt constellation (roughly south from my position) i looked right of that into open, unlit sky (no stars) and saw 4 orbs travelling fairly low to the ground going south west. they were incredibly dim lights that i never would have noticed from inside my car. at first i thought they were birds travelling in a delta formation, but then they started to move ahead and behind each other at random. the orbs maintained a straight flight path, but like i said, they were moving back and forth within an object moving southwest. it's really hard for me to compare it to anything.. if you had 4 rubber balls and dropped them lazily from your hands they would all hit the ground at different times (let's say). the orbs were bouncing back and forth. the 'craft' was invisible, or it was just too dark for me to spot, all i saw were the lights. it almost looked like a spotlight from the ground, but there were zero clouds to reflect any spotlight. 
i actually have a camera in my car now in case i see ufos, because i've seen 4 now within several months. i was only 15 feet from my car door, but as soon as i saw the shifting lights i was just kind of astonished. i've seen some weird footage of unusual lights, but never anything like these, and i was afraid that if i went to get my camera, the lights would be gone. after i had stared at the lights they just sort of vanished. kind of like someone turned down on a dimmer switch. 
i got my dslr out to at least try and get some long exposures, but i had no luck.
content.summary: 4 orbs moving back and forth within invisible craft flying away

content.detailedDescription:
I was driving south bound on u.S. hi-way 27. the sun had just set not that long before the sighting happened.I first saw a solid light in the sky descending, me first thought was that it was a plane landing since there is an airport not but 5 miles away from the hi-way. but i kept observing the light and realized that it was still descending but it had shifted coarse from the air port.  

at that point i was starting to feel a little worried. i thought maybe something was wrong with the plane? but just a few seconds later i realized this wasn't a plane at all. for a brief moment i thought it could be a helicopter, until this thing went right over the road and stopped quickly over a nearby tree line. now i know this is going to sound funny but i thought "what would fox mulder do?" 

so i pulled over in a near by median,got out of my car and immediately noticed it was a triangle shaped ufo! my jaw dropped and hit the floor. this thing was just hovering over a tree line right next to a busy hi-way! to my amazement i witnessed no other cars slowing down or stopping to observe this incredible moment. it had red and white lights on the bottom and sides of the craft. the red was blinking no different than you would see on a chopper or plane but the white lights, they seemed to 'pulse' in and out. 

the ufo continued to just hover there for a moment but it started moving again and it crossed the road again, it actually almost went right over me! that's when i started to get a little panicked. but i kept my cool because to be honest it was more intriguing than frightening. i try to keep a sense of wonder about the unknown or just science in general rather than fear it. so the craft started moving in a zig-zag pattern down the hi-way.I got back in my car and started following it but it picked up too much speed and altitude to continue pursuing it.

i hope that someone reads this and can contact me about it. this is the first time i've ever reported this sighting and would like some answers. and if you were wondering, no it didn't affect my car or me, nor did i experience a loss of time or contacted by any men in black. it is just something i feel fortunate enough to have witnessed.
content.summary: Black triangle shaped ufo

content.detailedDescription: I went outside into my backyard to smoke a cigarette around 12 midnight. i habitually look to the sky to see stars. it was overcast. for some reason i noticed a blue-white figure of some sort that appeared above the house diagonal to mine from the backyard over the roof. i got scared at first i thought it might be an invisible entity monitoring me. i noticed it was kind of invisible and you could not see it by looking at it directly. i could only see it through my peripheral vision so i had to look at an angle. i got closer and farther away and figured it was not an entity or it would have moved more as opposed to being stationary. i noticed it was a lot of small blue-white stars or spaceships shining through the clouds bunched up. they formed a tree like triangle pattern. occasionally some of the objects would move into different patterns. one looked like the peace symbol you do with your fingers. i saw them make a straight vertical line and i also saw other shapes i could not understand or make out. it was really hard to view them since it was out of my peripheral vision only, looking at them straight on would make them turn invisible or nearly invisible. they were very far away south west. probably from space shining through clouds. they eventually mostly disappeared.
content.summary: Many spaceships or stars shining through clouds

content.detailedDescription:
Was playing with neighborhood kids (8-10 witnesses) during summer break at around 2am. the ufo hovered just above the tree and house lines moving up the hill cutting over into another neighborhood. (moving west away from the 5 freeway at walking speed) (freeway and object distance about 150 yds apart) sighting went about 5 minutes until i chose to get my dslr camera. on return and travel uphill i lost sight of the craft.

the craft itself was a neon bright plasma/liquid like surface that had a constant but shifting textured surface. the craft was an oval shape about 30-50 ft. in diameter and gave off no heat or noise.

my conclusion is that it was a ufo that lost its cloak and descended to the treeline, just out of sight of the freeway traffic so that it could repair the issue. this may explain why i didn't see it again on my return.
content.summary: Variable plasma/liquid like surface in constant shift

content.detailedDescription: I was driving to work on interstate 70e at 7:05 am near the green castle indiana exit.  i saw in the sky ahead of me what at first glance ivthought it was one of those tall antennas with the lights.  i then realized the light i could seecwas not flashing like the ones on those antenna.  the object was hovering in place.  since i was driving i did not just stare at the object.  i once again trained my attention back to the object.  it was now beginning to move horizontally to the right from my perspective.  this lasted only a few seconds.  the object suddenly decended almost straight down into the treeline.  it moved so fast i expected to see smoke or something to begin to risecin the area it happen.  i did not see anything after that.  i later checked online news to see if there had been any flight accidents or meteor sighting.  nothing had been reported to my surprise.  i am a rational person with analytically inclined conclusions.  my reporting of this event was not taken lightly.  i cannot explain what i witnessed.
content.summary: Glowing stationary hover then horizontal travel then rapid vertical decent

content.detailedDescription:
I went outside for my afternoon break and strangely enough didn't sit under the canopy we have out there. looked up and thought at first it was a strange plane, i thought it was really high up but had trouble seeing wings. planes in portland you usually see fairly low and heading to the airport. then i thought this plane must just be passing by. the more i looked the more it looked like a hotdog shape that was silver but had a dark band around the middle of it. suddenly it looked a little different, like the light was reflecting off it differently, and then it completely dissapeared. i think now it may have been changing shape. i still wasn't convinced my eyes weren't playing tricks on me, but right after that two planes came along that looked smaller, and i could clearly see their wings. they also had trails out of the back, but the other object didn't. then a helicopter came by from the other direction. 
it moved so slowly and steadily it could have been a plane, but once it was gone it was 100% gone, i didn't see it fade away. i was pretty excited to see it because i have had an experience before with a ufo but it was a totally different experience during a camping trip and i didn't ever actually see the ufo, just the light from it. i have been doing a lot of studying on ufo and abduction lately, so i have been spending more time looking up into the sky. it was cool to finally see one in day light from a distance.

content.detailedDescription: It was a little after 10pm on a friday night, it was my friend and i in my car and we were parked right beside a bridge waiting to meet another friend.  i just pulled in to park so we could wait and before i could even put my car in park i see an object in the sky.  at first i thought it was someone who lived beside the river shinning a spot light or even a boat with a spot light, but it was just so spherical in shape and it was bright.  this thing was just hovering right over the river moving from left to right slowly.  i was left speechless watching the mysterious object just slowly start going towards the sky and then in the blink of an eye it melted like a tear drop in the sky. as soon as the object just vanished i shouted to my friend did you see that but unfortunately she was on her phone not paying any attention to what was going on.  it all lasted approximately 30 seconds at most.   something is out there flying in the sky and i cannot explain it but it clearly had camouflage cloaking.  i have always believed that there is life out there i just never thought i would see it with my own eyes.  something is out there in the sky for sure.

content.detailedDescription:
On the above date and time i (alone) was driving/traveling east on maryland ave to central ave (phoenix, az) during rush hour traffic after being detoured twice by two different auto accidents to alternate route of surface streets i selected.  while going eastbound on maryland to central avenue (north) i observed 3 red-orange orbs in a triangle formation directly in front of me with no noise emitting from them.  the dominate/larger orb (softball size) was at the top of triangle formation while the other two (tip and bottom) were smaller (orange size). they were glowing and appeared to be pulsating to my human eyes of which i was wearing my prescription glasses for night driving.   the distance in the sky from me was approximately 1000-1500 feet away.  i noticed no other vehicles appeared to notice them except for myself.

when i approached maryland/central avenue i turned northbound until i reached dunlap ave.  during this time traveling northbound the 3-orbs moved their position and remained in my front view as i continued driving.  once i reached dunlap avenue i turned left heading westbound to the black canyon freeway/i-17 northbound to commute home to camp verde, az, which is approximately 93 miles away (rural community). the 3-orbs continued to stay constant ahead of me as i traveled westbound to the freeway.

upon entering the freeway northbound off of dunlap the 3-orbs remained  within my front view but changed position/formation:  the dominant larger orb was at an 11 o'clock position, the bottom orb remained below dominant at 9-10 o'clock position (northern sky direction). while the orb that was the tip position moved drastically away from the other two and was a 2 o'clock position to my right (more east sky direction).  also, they had changed colors now white/silver, with still no noise emitting as i kept my window down. throughout my trip home i almost drove off the road several times as i continued to watch them.  i then stopped off at anthem (north suburb/phoenix) gas station for a restroom break since my commute home (camp verde) would be another 45 minutes (approximately).

i came out of the restroom got into my car taking the access road back onto i-17 northbound when i noticed the lights remained fixed in the sky at their same position as if waiting for me.  i then spoke to the glowing white/silver orbs in the sky asking them if they were guiding me safely home.  i traveled i-17 northbound continuing my conversation with them in regards to reaching my destination safely to my son who was at home alone. the 3-orbs remained constantly traveling with me of same position in the sky.  

prior to coming into the verde valley i was to ascend, travel a small mountain terrain this is when i called my son to inform of experience and asked him to go outside and look into the sky of stated direction of 3-orb position.  estimated time to arrive home was 10 minutes.  once out of mountain terrain i exited off the 260-northbound (cottonwood/camp verde exit) with the 3-orbs still remaining with me.

i headed northbound-260 for approximately 3-5 miles to the yavapai-apache nation (tunalii district) where i reside.  the 3 white/silver orbs stayed with me until i reached my driveway.  once home my son came out to inform that he saw nothing.  i suggest we go out to the backyard where it is pitch black and look at the sky.  we went to the backyard and saw nothing.  then we went to the front driveway where the 3-orbs were in the sky pulsating in same directional position.  i informed the 3-orbs i was home safely and introduced them to my son who witnessed the event.  the east direction orb disappeared. the little orb that was accompanying dominant orb flew north disappearing in the night sky. while the dominant white/silver orb flew towards us (approximately 500 ft) with an asension 4-pointed star design/craft change formation then flew abruptly away towards sedona, az. 

on november 14, 2015, an elongated 4 fingerprint impression was left on my dusy kitchenette table of which i have taken photos. 

december 12, 2015, i have received 2nd impressions of two fingers.  photos were taken.
content.summary: Observed 3 red-orange orbs triangle shape in the city then followed me up north to camp verde

content.detailedDescription:
The weird lightning was a trigger of sorts. it seemed it was over anaheim stadium and appered to have flashed down instead of up a few times that night. i saw that same thing in fort lauderdale, fl just before hurricane micheal destroyed haiti in the 90's. both times, it triggered adrenaline rushes for unknown reasons.  a caveat: my mental state was deeply depressed and traumatized from other human issues at the time and i realize this may effect my credibility. please hear me out anyway. 

this was right before 9-11 on july 3, 2001 and there was seriously weird moods and vibes in the air everywhere--on the news and radio in particular. i was becoming increasingly sensitive to everything re: other peoples' moods and agitation. i was becoming agitated and apocalyptic myself. i do not really know why. that night, i began to think uncharacteristic thoughts that we were about to be attacked and i had to follow clues. the weird lightning triggered a march of sorts. my head felt electrified, as if it were operational in its entirely. overwhelming.


i landed myself in a psych-ward and i do hold myself fully accountable.  ....Whatever it was also seemed to be guiding me to march down the middle of the freeway saluting patriotically, then by a railroad track to then strip to my sneakers in all my naked in-glory to again salute a passing train. i thought i somehow stopped a war. later, i began to experience thoughts of the "winning"/superior human races (mine of course) and how it will survive the coming "apocalypse"(i swear i am not racist and reject this as tripe whole-hardheartedly now), i ranted about how we are at war with the middle east and it had to do with my birthday (11-9-73), i also ranted about how i am part alien, my brain felt completely "turned on", my eyes felt bulgy,and something was in my head "guiding" me. i also felt a religious pressure, that i was some sort of "chosen" prophet and had a duty to perform for the human race. i was also required to become a strict religious devout... it felt as though two sides were fighting over my mind. these were not voices, they were impressions--abstract thoughts. in short...I lost my damn mind. i smoked a small amount of grass hours before, but i really think this is above and beyond the effects of pot.I now believe my weakened mental state and resulting malnutrition opened me up to some sort of psychic assault? it remains unclear from what exactly. something in that lightning storm effected me too. i realize i handled myself poorly, but truly feel there is something here. my entire belief system slowly re-invented itself from this point on. 

no history of insanity runs in my family and has never happened before or since that particular year of recovery. they diagnosed me as schizo-effective, and bipolar. i have since been re-diagnosed as having had ptsd due to other things and am perfectly healthy currently.

i flushed the meds soon after and sought to get my mind/body happy and healthy again. that was my cure for certain. i also began my research into the rabbit-hole of ufo's, spirits, tricksters, etc. a few years later. i found many, many similar cases. the racial and religious agitation is one notable, historical similarity. people also love to believe they are special and needed to save the world. it is an easy point of manipulation for most. some ufo websites attract the "crazies", but i have noticed some of them ranting similar things as what i was. they need help and i found all of them are in weakened psychological/physical states--wide open for this kind of assault.

i am also an artist/musician. we tend to be sensitive to this? most of us are diagnosed with bipolar disorder at the slightest sign of depression. i often wonder......Those drugs are terrible. when i focused on my health, all signs of mental illness, invasion, or whatever you wish to call it disappeared and no further psychological oppression has been allowed. education is power. 

anyway, i consider my experience to be an awakening of sorts and i felt it was time to share what i learned with you. john keel also mentions the racial agitation, telepathy, religious oppression and general nonsense information we sometime receive, in his books "our haunted planet" and "operation trojan horse". he also notes the similarities in reports of ufo's, historical fairy reports, airships of the 1800's all culturally relevant for the times. but they are similar in content.  digging john mack, james redfield, "what the bleep do we know" as well as many other researchers, thinkers and works out there.  telepathic contact is quite common, it turns out. what a strange reality this turned out to be! we are slowly piecing it together. 

it is my sincere hope that my story is a contribution to the puzzle. thank you for all your wonderful and hard work. my the force be with you!


sincerely,
kristen johansen
content.summary: Weird lightning, thoughts that absolutely were not mine, premonitions, junk

content.detailedDescription: They move across the sky all the time. i've seen many before. my best sighting was last year at the park at night when i was chilling with my friends and sitting on the swing looking at the sky to see if i can spot any weird objects moving through the sky, and i did. it was an orange light moving slowly across the sky but in a weird movement, then it flew off with a high speed. the one i am reporting now was moving across the sky, it looked close enough to be in out atmosphere. it had no blinking lights and fitted the description of a ufo. i looked at it fly across the sky. every day and night i look in our atmosphere to see if i can spot another ufo. please believe me as i would put my right hand on the bible because i am telling the truth. i keep record of sightings e.G date, time, year and month and i describe it also. i would like to hear from you guys again. my friends are also witnesses as i show them where the ufo is when i see it.
content.summary: I have been seing objects fly across the sky from 21.01.2016 until 25.01.2016 (tonight). there are no flashing lights and they move, hover and take off very fast. i've never seen anything like it before. i believe in ufos, please believe me.
